259
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:20,800
Hey.

260
00:19:22,820 --> 00:19:24,700
You heard that, didn't you?

261
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:39,420
That girl...

262
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:42,020
I think Tsubaki calls her Sakura.

263
00:19:42,020 --> 00:19:45,420
I think everyone thinks it's Sakura.

264
00:19:46,060 --> 00:19:47,420
